539
00:35:42,932 --> 00:35:45,017
Stop it! Please!

540
00:35:51,649 --> 00:35:52,817
Mommy!

541
00:36:00,867 --> 00:36:01,951
Mommy!

542
00:36:09,834 --> 00:36:11,085
Help.

