00:50:48,170 --> 00:50:50,589
There's a time to lose control.

734
00:50:50,672 --> 00:50:53,383
It's worse if you do that
after you get older.

735
00:50:54,176 --> 00:50:55,177
Okay?

736
00:50:55,969 --> 00:50:57,220
This is the time

737
00:50:58,555 --> 00:50:59,890
