744
00:51:39,012 --> 00:51:42,307
I'll take the spicy chicken home too.

745
00:51:44,935 --> 00:51:47,521
Half fried, half spicy. Half and half.

746
00:52:01,284 --> 00:52:02,369
Ouch.

