to do the dishes.

786
00:58:28,046 --> 00:58:29,547
Sit down and get some rest.

787
00:58:30,131 --> 00:58:31,883
Move. I'll do it.

788
00:58:31,966 --> 00:58:34,385
You'll do it for life
once you get married. Don't do it now.

789
00:58:34,969 --> 00:58:37,055
